name: Manulife Smart Dividend ETF
longDescription: The Fund seeks to provide a combination of income and long-term capital appreciation. The Fund will invest primarily in a diversified portfolio of Canadian dividend paying securities.
fulldescription: The Fund seeks to provide a combination of income and long-term capital appreciation. The Fund will invest primarily in a diversified portfolio of Canadian dividend paying securities. The portfolio advisor employs a proprietary quality dividend screen to select securities that have high and sustainable dividends or dividends that are expected to grow over time and optimizes the Fund by allocating proportionally more assets to securities that have higher potential risk-adjusted returns
